    "title": "Urgent Opening Financial Analyst at SBI Life Insurance International Enterprises",
    "description": "Grow your career with SBI Life Insurance International Enterprises! We are hiring a Financial Analyst for our Ahmedabad team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout SBI Life Insurance International Enterprises:\nSBI Life Insurance International Enterprises is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage accounts payable and accounts receivable functions\n• Monitor market trends and provide investment recommendations\n• Prepare and analyze financial statements, reports, and budgets\n• Develop financial models and projections for business planning\n• Monitor financial performance against targets and provide variance analysis\n• Maintain general ledger and ensure accurate bookkeeping\n• Implement and maintain internal controls and audit procedures\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBBS / MD / MS from recognized medical college\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in SQL\n• Proficiency in Risk Management\n• Proficiency in Due Diligence\n• Proficiency in IFRS\n• Proficiency in SAP FICO\n• Proficiency in Credit Analysis\n• Proficiency in QuickBooks\n• Proficiency in Financial Reporting\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Learning & development budget\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ahmedabad, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with SBI Life Insurance International Enterprises!",
